            array('id' => '65','post_id' => '26','key' => 'description','value' => '<p>Welcome to AgroVest, an agricultural investment platform connecting investors with opportunities in the agricultural sector. By accessing or using our platform, you agree to comply with and be bound by the following terms and conditions. Please read these terms carefully before using our services.</p>
<br>
